{"tid":2188233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"已逝雪莉紀錄片公開⋯親母哽咽：媽媽來晚了　少時蒂芬妮爆哭","createTime":"2020-09-04T06:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:21:15.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a4ad8e6f36e587e9b96a476b9e146763821cd88e","tid":2188233,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"南韓已逝女星雪莉於2019年輕生離世，生命就此停到25歲，事隔1年時間，仍有許多粉絲深深思念著她，感到無限惋惜。她去世之後，電視台MBC曾表示將會製作她的紀錄片，採訪她身邊的友人、親人，但遭到各界反對，直到近期才正式訂下播出日期，官方4日公開一則30秒左右的短版預告，雪莉的媽媽罕見入鏡，並流下眼淚表示「媽媽來晚了，很抱歉。」預告片公開後，令人感傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5118/d5118751.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5118%2Fd5118751.jpg&h=b1d86746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MBC當時發布要製作已逝雪莉紀錄片的消息時，遭到許多反彈聲浪。（圖／翻攝自MBC Youtube）<br />\n<br />\n電視台MBC於7月底公開一則消息，表示將會製作關於雪莉的紀錄片，內容將以採訪雪莉身邊的親友以及她的故事為主軸，藉此哀悼故人離世。然而，當時消息公開後，遭到很多粉絲反彈表示「不要在傷口上灑鹽」、「不要消費死者」，後續相關的播放日期也就不了了之。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5118/d5118747.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5118%2Fd5118747.jpg&h=60cc7a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼紀錄片採訪到雪莉的媽媽以及少時成員蒂芬妮。（圖／翻攝自MBC Youtube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5118/d5118748.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5118%2Fd5118748.jpg&h=b9ec682e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒想到，事隔近2個月，MBC於4日突如其來公開一則30秒左右的短版預告，內容曝光雪莉幼時開朗活潑的樣子，以及她推出個人專輯時笑著表示「我會努力地好好活下去」，接著，雪莉的媽媽罕見現身哭著說道「媽媽太晚來了抱歉」，她的昔日同事少時蒂芬妮也在鏡頭前哽咽：「對於在她身旁卻沒能有更深入的對話，感到抱歉。」最後，畫面穿插著雪莉生前說過的話「唯獨對我戴著有色眼鏡的人很多」、「不要誤會我，我不是壞人」，短短30秒的預告片令人鼻酸，網路評論掀起正反意見，該紀錄片預計在10日晚間10點50分播岀（台灣時間晚間9點50分）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3MJcW65gO2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3MJcW65gO2A&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=c1beff1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3MJcW65gO2A</a>"},{"pid":"ce81cdf7604c46a3a895217546fee3a2e1bdda9b","tid":2188233,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"幾淫"},{"pid":"6d21a8554cfdad2b0b07e60565e40a966d80dbb9","tid":2188233,"uid":77959,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:28:53.000Z","msg":"來晚了分遺產？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e56760c23dfa2112f6914e65e28e97a1eed1c6","tid":2188233,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"冇揾iu?"},{"pid":"ed43fdb30030afc135c2ebe9f2312dc203d499bd","tid":2188233,"uid":220760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e56760c23dfa2112f6914e65e28e97a1eed1c6","tid":2188233,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"冇揾iu?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"都唔知佢會唔會出黎講"},{"pid":"79601803266a457c93cfe65079954441d75a2fdd","tid":2188233,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"79e56760c23dfa2112f6914e65e28e97a1eed1c6","tid":2188233,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"冇揾iu?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"IU唔似金希澈咁長期消費死者"},{"pid":"b6570e0133ec2e8ed404d4e4984fd2a6ef7790be","tid":2188233,"uid":357588,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79601803266a457c93cfe65079954441d75a2fdd","tid":2188233,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"79e56760c23dfa2112f6914e65e28e97a1eed1c6","tid":2188233,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"冇揾iu?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"IU唔似金希澈咁長期消費死者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"但係希澈唔係養埋雪莉隻貓咩"},{"pid":"19ef13403d4f20dd6b19bf121d31462219ee4745","tid":2188233,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6570e0133ec2e8ed404d4e4984fd2a6ef7790be","tid":2188233,"uid":357588,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79601803266a457c93cfe65079954441d75a2fdd","tid":2188233,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"79e56760c23dfa2112f6914e65e28e97a1eed1c6","tid":2188233,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"冇揾iu?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"IU唔似金希澈咁長期消費死者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"但係希澈唔係養埋雪莉隻貓咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"消費死者姐 日撚日提 都未見過第2個好似佢隔一排又彈出黎"},{"pid":"9c734e0b1be16a6b47e2bf8dce962fe8078406a5","tid":2188233,"uid":68678,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"咁jessica 離團個陣 呀蒂芬妮有冇爆哭？"},{"pid":"3426a8b62d1d2da3b3f78861156e21565573f046","tid":2188233,"uid":22210,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c734e0b1be16a6b47e2bf8dce962fe8078406a5","tid":2188233,"uid":68678,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"咁jessica 離團個陣 呀蒂芬妮有冇爆哭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"收皮喇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我小學四年級的時候來到首爾，五年級的時候搬進宿舍和泰妍歐尼Tiffany歐尼一起，她們照顧著我，我一直跟著她們。我真的很愛我的歐尼們，我是一個人來的首爾，除了泰妍歐尼和Tiffany歐尼，我沒有什麼人可以傾述依靠&hellip;曾經害怕出道以後我們會分開，真的很感謝歐尼，我出道以後也一直照顧著我」"},{"pid":"476f082d2847397036364d44b1831a877b0ab6c2","tid":2188233,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}